      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/ilhan-omar",
      "text": "The United States should lead by example, not exempt itself from the standards it expects everyone else to follow. In 2022, I introduced a resolution calling on the United States to join the ICC because I believe America should stand with victims of atrocities, defend human",
