      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/ilhan-omar",
      "text": "Secretary Rubio claims that the ICC poses ‘an intolerable threat to U.S. sovereignty’ and that American servicemembers could be prosecuted simply for serving our country. That is simply not true.",
